Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.35,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Draw your blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:10.47,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If we see it, it'll only be for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:18.49,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:33.30,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.29,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,In these trees, there's no way to \Nforesee and evade its attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:37.34,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,It'll catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.51,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, let's switch to Maneuver Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.39,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:44.89,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:46.82,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements from the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:04.62,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, your orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:05.79,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:07.29,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:08.99,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,We should kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.78,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it {\i1}will{\i0} catch up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:11.92,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,We kill it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:14.20,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we came to this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:16.18,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:18.29,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:23.50,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, cover your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:17.00,Title,Ar,0000,0000,0000,,Bite \N 57th Expedition Beyond the Walls (3)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.51,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,A noise grenade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.16,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What is your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:32.52,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,To just let yourself be swayed by whatever \Nyou're feeling at the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.70,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.52,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Our squad's job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:40.66,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,is to keep the brat from getting \Na single scratch on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.03,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it costs our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.16,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't to keep watch on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:52.83,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,We keep going on our horses, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.14,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:58.17,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going? For how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.40,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,And it's right on top of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.18,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:05.97,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,The reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.43,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't help, they'll be wiped out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.27,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Eren, eyes on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.48,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.56,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your pace up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.10,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Stay at top speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:15.94,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:21.49,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,If Squad Levi doesn't defeat it, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.16,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Another one's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:30.16,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe we could've saved him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.58,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,One's still fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.92,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,We could still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.25,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Eren, eyes back on the road! Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.34,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to look away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.30,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,To abandon my comrades and run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.80,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.51,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Obey the Captain's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.85,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why we're leaving them to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.66,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Or why he won't explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.52,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.94,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the Captain decided \Nthe reason should not be explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.90,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't understand because you're still green!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.76,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it, then shut up and obey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:09.78,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.00,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.13,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I relying on others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.80,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,I can just fight on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.09,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:34.14,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You're only allowed to do that \Nif your life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.81,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You promised us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.02,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:43.15,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.32,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.56,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.58,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,He's a real monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.41,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,And it has nothing to do with his Titan power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.85,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what power you use to suppress him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.13,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what cage you put him in,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:07.50,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,he will never submit to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.84,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,417)}I just want to slaughter the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:17.72,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Eren, the difference between your \Ndecision and ours is experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.48,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to rely on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.82,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.36,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or believe in the Survey Corps and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.66,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.19,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.54,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I can believe in my own abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.38,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,or the choices of companions I trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.88,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But no one ever knows how it will turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:51.59,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,So choose for yourself whichever \Ndecision you'll regret least.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.15,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.57,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:24.24,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with a way that'd only half-kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.30,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:32.29,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd only be able to stop \Nyou as a Titan if I killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:36.18,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But this method would only badly wound you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.22,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it relies on the squad's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:44.42,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,The idea is to cut you right out of the Titan's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:48.81,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,We'd end up cutting the ends \Nof your arms and legs off,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.38,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,but they'd just grow back like a lizard's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.65,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.41,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.99,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how they grow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.62,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some other way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:07.30,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying you don't want there \Nto be any danger or sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.00,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.84,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Then just resolve yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.68,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,We will, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.25,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,The danger for us is that you might kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:17.30,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.56,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.52,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, I can do experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.90,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's very risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.94,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean that we \Ncan't use him to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.82,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I can be in charge of planning this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.02,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Eren, if there's something \Nyou don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.24,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,learn to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:43.28,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's well worth any risk to our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.62,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:53.34,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,When it's prepared, I'll use the \Nsmoke round to notify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.01,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,After that, any decisions are up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.10,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:04.79,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,This dried-up well could hold \Neven a mindless Titan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.89,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.66,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.80,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,Since I sealed the wall, I haven't \Ntried to control the Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:22.02,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose control, Squad Levi \Nmight kill me this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.54,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Did he not see the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:34.88,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:39.15,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,His ability just isn't that reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.89,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Eren! We're calling it quits for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.65,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.32,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.54,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become a Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:08.08,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,So your self-inflicted bite wounds on \Nyour hands aren't healing, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.30,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.74,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't transform into a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our main goal of sealing Wall Maria is off the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.39,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.01,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.65,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:29.64,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get you down, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.67,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:35.57,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it just means you're \Nmore human than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.81,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Better than rushing into \Nsomething and getting killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.70,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.22,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:46.75,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:52.56,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.54,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,Are they okay with my being \Nunable to turn into a Titan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:07.58,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:08.67,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:22.97,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:23.81,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.12,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What was that explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.49,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.38,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.18,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Levi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:43.81,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.43,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I said to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:08.95,Eyecatch1A,,0000,0000,0000,,Information We Can Share So Far:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:08.95,Eyecatch1,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Rounds (1) \NSignal rounds fired by small handguns using gunpowder. \NA small tube, with the round, is swapped out each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:13.96,Eyecatch2A,,0000,0000,0000,,Information We Can Share So Far:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:13.96,Eyecatch2,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Rounds (2) \NThe signal color changes per message: \NRed — Titan sighted. \NGreen — Change course. \N Black — Aberrant sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.34,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,What? What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:33.69,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.48,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:36.98,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.31,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Why now? Without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:40.03,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:41.03,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Eldo, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.27,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,Answer him, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.24,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.78,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:51.79,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Prove you're not our enemy, humanity's enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.60,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Prove it! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.33,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,That is your responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.86,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to make a single move with that arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.63,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut off your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.10,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it... I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.13,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.07,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oluo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.75,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, get away from Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.35,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.28,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're the ones who should get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:12.81,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.60,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.64,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,My intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.69,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.92,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.39,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.52,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,No sudden movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.19,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Prove it to me, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.12,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.83,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Answer us! You think we can't kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.00,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.83,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:26.90,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:27.87,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.80,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Are you humanity's—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.24,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Please shut up for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.71,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:43.09,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Can I touch that arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.18,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.64,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.89,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.13,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.77,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's... hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.66,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Without the skin, it's really damned hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.57,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievably hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.40,Default,Mog,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.69,Default,Mog,0000,0000,0000,,you're too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.40,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you feel it's hot, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.48,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel where the right hand connects?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.35,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.41,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.22,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,If I just pull out this hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.21,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.74,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:21.92,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.00,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.18,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Eren... That was too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.64,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I still wanted to investigate some things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:45.90,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.15,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:59.62,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,324)}Not... Not so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:10.56,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Until I saw that they were actually ready \Nto kill me, I didn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.49,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,That they doubted me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.44,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.10,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I chose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.85,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,People say you only truly become a \Nfull member of the Survey Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after making it back alive from a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But whenever you fight the Titans, \Nyou never have enough information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:34.55,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many situations you just \Ncan't anticipate, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.00,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,They've had to cultivate the \Nability to take quick action
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.82,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,and to make ruthless decisions by assuming \Nthe worse case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:46.25,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean they've become heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:51.38,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they felt nothing when \Nthey turned their swords on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.82,Default,Mo,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Levi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.80,Default,Mo,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Leader Hanji wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.21,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Take a long crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.27,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it was pleasantly quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:08.33,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure what to tell the brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.55,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.60,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.28,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,A teaspoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.24,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:21.52,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The right Titan hand Eren \Ncreated was holding this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:25.50,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Like this, between its index finger and thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.21,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to imagine that was an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,And for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the heat and pressure didn't \Nwarp the spoon at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.01,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Anything come to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.56,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to pick it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.27,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I transformed right after.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.85,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:50.61,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That may explain why you couldn't transform earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:53.87,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,"Kill the Titans."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.41,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,"Block the cannon shell."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.49,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,"Lift the boulder."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:02.73,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,In each case, you had a clear \Ngoal before you transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,My theory is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:08.22,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,that your self-inflicted injury \Nprobably isn't the sole trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.80,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You may need some goal, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:15.10,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that when I turned into a Titan this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was like when I blocked that cannon shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.35,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.94,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,I turned into a Titan to pick up a spoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.24,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:32.74,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you didn't deliberately \Nchange without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.26,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.71,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.79,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.44,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:02.29,Default,El,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you can bite through, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.98,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,We made the wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.51,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,This is a small price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.23,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it makes a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.14,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping you under control is our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.80,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.03,Default,O,0000,0000,0000,,So don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.99,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.54,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,We've been so jumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.92,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,You must be disappointed in our stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.31,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,However, even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:33.86,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to rely on you. \NAnd we want you to rely on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.24,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:44.22,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.07,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.74,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking too long! Decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.03,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.42,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.84,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.97,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Target is accelerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:28.75,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.11,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,We will outrun it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:36.21,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to outrun it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:40.80,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep running away, it'll stomp us all flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.03,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.29,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,We might all die,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.54,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,but everyone chose to go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.04,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it meant abandoning our comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:56.35,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Levi has been looking \Nforward this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.60,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,And the rest of the squad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.55,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,believe in him, and put all their trust in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:07.06,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in them, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.06,Default - italics,E,0000,0000,0000,,Like they
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.28,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,believed in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.14,Default,Er,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:54.07,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Advance a bit farther, tether the horses,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and switch to Maneuver Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.02,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,You guys will be off on your own for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.13,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Eldo, lead the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:04.88,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're a good distance away \Nfrom the Titan, hide Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.20,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Take my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.37,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,He can't intend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:16.65,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,to take that Titan alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.54,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Eren? See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.68,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,We caught that Titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:28.14,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of the Survey Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.76,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us, fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.78,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.62,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.07,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's stopped moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:43.11,Default,Er,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lower our guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.34,Default,Er,0000,0000,0000,,But you did well, leading it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:53.66,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Men in the rearguard squads died \Nbuying us the time we needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:56.46,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't have done it without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.25,Default,Er,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.76,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:06.43,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to them, we'll be able \Nto see who's inside this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:11.99,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they haven't pissed themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:59.96,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Erwin Smith's secret plan was \Nto capture the Female Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:05.38,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The aces of the Survey Corps try \Nto reveal its true identity, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:07.83,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Erwin Smith \N57th Expedition Beyond the Walls (4)
